TITLE.Word LTR 20: Your Confirmation of Permanent Residence (COPR) has been issued

BODY.Word LTR 20:
We have finished reviewing your application.
We have issued your Confirmation of Permanent Residence (COPR). Please do not sign the COPR until instructed to do so by an immigration officer at landing.
You must complete your landing to confirm your status as a permanent resident of Canada before the expiry date on your COPR.
Please read the message we sent you for more details.
BODY.Auto E-mail 111:
We sent you a message with instructions on how to submit your fingerprints and photo. Please complete this by the date shown in your message.
**If you already completed your biometrics, please ignore this message. There is a delay between when we receive your information and when this tool is updated.

BODY.INITIAL: We received your application and we’re checking to make sure you’ve submitted all the required forms and documents on the document checklist. If your application is incomplete, we’ll return it to you without processing it. If your application has all the requested forms and documents, you’ll get a message confirming we’ve accepted your application for processing.
BODY.AOR: We sent you a message telling you we received your application. We have now officially started processing your application.
BODY.BIOMETRICS: We sent you a message with instructions on how to submit your fingerprints and photo. Please complete this by the date shown in your message.
BODY.BIOMETRIC_FEES: We sent you a message with instructions on how to pay your biometric fees. Once we’ve processed your payment, we’ll send instructions on when and how to give your biometrics. Please complete by the date shown in your message.
BODY.COPR_ISSUED: We have issued your Confirmation of Permanent Residence (COPR). Read the message we sent you for more details.
BODY.DNA: We sent you a message with instructions to collect DNA samples. Please book your test by the date shown in your message.
BODY.ELIG_DEC: Read the message we sent you about this decision.
BODY.MED_REPORT: We sent you a request to complete a medical exam. Read the message for more details.
BODY.MED_ADD: We received your immigration medical exam results, but we need more information to complete the assessment. Please follow the instructions in the message we sent you.
BODY.MED_RESULT: We received your immigration medical exam results. We sent you an important message with further information on your results.
BODY.PREARRIVAL: We sent you a message about free [pre-arrival services](https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/new-immigrants/new-life-canada/pre-arrival-services.html) that you can now use. These services are available to you before you arrive and are meant to help prepare for and adjust to life in Canada.
BODY.PR_AUTH: Please refer to the message we sent you for details.
BODY.REFUND_FEES: Read the message we sent you for more details about the fees refund for this application.
BODY.SPR_DEC: Please refer to the message we sent you about this decision.
BODY.TRANSFERRED: Your application has been transferred to another office for continued processing. Read the message we sent you for more details.
BODY.WITHDRAWN: Your application has been withdrawn. Read the message we sent you for more details.
BODY.OTHER: Read the message carefully and take appropriate action as necessary.
